===Noun===

'''evaporation'''

#The [[process]] by which any [[substance]] is converted from the [[liquid]] to the [[gas|gaseous]] state.
#The [[transformation]] of a portion of a [[fluid]] into [[vapor]], in order to obtain the fixed [[matter]] contained in it in a state of greater [[concentration]].
#That which is evaporated; vapor.
